2
00:01:06,050 --> 00:01:07,470
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,320
Chen Jing'an,

4
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:10,930
what's your take

5
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:13,180
on puppy love?

6
00:01:14,020 --> 00:01:14,860
Puppy love?

7
00:01:19,340 --> 00:01:20,640
Well,

8
00:01:21,190 --> 00:01:22,230
I think

9
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,100
having a crush on someone

10
00:01:24,350 --> 00:01:25,720
is pretty normal

11
00:01:26,050 --> 00:01:27,430
at our age.

12
00:01:30,010 --> 00:01:30,850
So...

13
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,800
do you like anyone?

14
00:01:37,260 --> 00:01:38,100
No.

15
00:01:38,550 --> 00:01:39,390
Really?

16
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:41,980
What about you?

17
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:43,160
Is there anyone

18
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,800
you have a soft spot for?

19
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,510
Of course not.

20
00:01:55,930 --> 00:01:56,770
Well,

21
00:01:56,890 --> 00:01:57,730
if...

22
00:01:57,930 --> 00:01:59,600
you did like someone,

23
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,510
would you date her?

24
00:02:04,890 --> 00:02:05,730
No way.

25
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:10,980
Come on,

26
00:02:12,140 --> 00:02:13,600
you're in high school now.

27
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:16,050
You should know

28
00:02:16,100 --> 00:02:17,220
what's appropriate.

29
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:21,300
You look unsure.

30
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:22,780
I didn't.

31
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,180
You'd better mean that.

32
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:27,600
If I find out you're dating someone,

33
00:02:28,050 --> 00:02:29,390
you're doomed.

34
00:02:30,220 --> 00:02:31,350
I know.

35
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:33,290
Also,

36
00:02:33,290 --> 00:02:35,300
no more hanging out with Li Minqiu.

37
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,480
Alright.

38
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,520
Wait here.

39
00:03:07,180 --> 00:03:08,630
Why are you here?

40
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,720
Chen Jing'an, I came to apologize.

41
00:03:10,970 --> 00:03:12,640
Look, I bought you snacks.

42
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:19,020
What's wrong?

43
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,510
Nothing.

44
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:21,890
I wanted to say sorry

45
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,240
for hitting you yesterday.

46
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,140
I'm sorry.

47
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,720
I asked around about your place

48
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,390
and came here to apologize.

49
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:28,720
These are all for you.

50
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:31,300
With all these snacks,

51
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:32,680
can you forgive me?

52
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,310
And

53
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,430
can you please

54
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:37,100
explain to Niannian?

55
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,640
It's misunderstanding.

56
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:40,470
You can rely on me.

57
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,740
If anyone bothers you,

58
00:03:41,740 --> 00:03:42,550
just tell me.

59
00:04:03,470 --> 00:04:04,430
Where did you get these?

60
00:04:06,930 --> 00:04:08,390
Tian Ye bought them

61
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,850
as an apology.

62
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,760
Didn't he give you

63
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,600
medicine yesterday?

64
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,100
He said it wasn't enough,

65
00:04:17,470 --> 00:04:19,220
so he got snacks.

66
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,850
But he doesn't live here.

67
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,430
So he came all the way for this.

68
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,470
Want some?

69
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,520
No.

70
00:04:38,350 --> 00:04:39,190
Chen Jing'an,

71
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:41,720
don't forget your promise.

72
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:47,390
Your roundabout way

73
00:04:49,010 --> 00:04:50,720
is quite nice.

74
00:04:50,930 --> 00:04:52,720
What's your next move?

75
00:04:54,010 --> 00:04:54,970
What roundabout way?

76
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,720
What puzzle is that?

77
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:59,390
Don't play dumb with me.

78
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:01,430
I know everything.

79
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,720
I always thought

80
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,470
you should be more forward.

81
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,970
Starting with Chen Jing'an

82
00:05:08,970 --> 00:05:10,300
is actually smart.

83
00:05:11,050 --> 00:05:12,050
(What?)

84
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,550
(Starting with me?)

85
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:15,850
(What does she mean?)

86
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:17,640
So what's your next move?

87
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,760
Next move?

88
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,260
No next move.

89
00:05:23,140 --> 00:05:23,980
Niannian!

90
00:05:27,470 --> 00:05:29,640
Yesterday was a good start.

91
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:32,050
Why hold yourself back now?

92
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:36,850
Niannian! Niannian, wait for me.

93
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:39,980
You order.

94
00:05:40,660 --> 00:05:41,510
Hurry.

95
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,430
My turn now.

96
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,890
- Can you do it?
- Don't distract me.

97
00:05:44,890 --> 00:05:46,010
- My turn.
- Let me try!

98
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,050
You two can't do this.

99
00:05:48,050 --> 00:05:48,930
Are you any good?

100
00:05:48,930 --> 00:05:49,930
Better than you.

101
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:51,760
- Not me.
- Beat him.

102
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,970
What are you playing?

103
00:05:57,100 --> 00:05:57,940
Chen Jing'an,

104
00:05:58,260 --> 00:05:59,220
since when are you rich?

105
00:05:59,850 --> 00:06:01,800
It's the first time
you've bought so many snacks.

106
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:02,970
Is it because

107
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,760
I played basketball with you

108
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,220
and you were so touched?

109
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,720
Yes, just for you.

110
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:11,510
I know you love me.

111
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,930
- You're welcome.
- Lots of love.

112
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,890
Chen Jing'an's treat.

113
00:06:18,050 --> 00:06:18,970
Thank you, Princess.

114
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:29,550
Thanks, I'm good.

115
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,600
It's okay,

116
00:06:30,890 --> 00:06:31,760
I'll save it for you.

117
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:45,690
Alright, class.

118
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,260
Let's look at this question.

119
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,180
The solution approach

120
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:51,600
will be key for the monthly exam.

121
00:06:52,010 --> 00:06:54,220
Master this method

122
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:55,390
and you'll gain

123
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:56,640
at least 10 more points.

124
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,640
Tian Ye,

125
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,470
explain the solution.

126
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:13,100
This question...

127
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:15,140
This question...

128
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,480
Put your hand down.

129
00:07:17,890 --> 00:07:18,730
Down!

130
00:07:28,850 --> 00:07:29,690
Tian Ye!

131
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,800
Let's decide

132
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:37,800
what to eat first.

133
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:41,850
Niannian, look!

134
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:43,260
It's Chen Jing'an.

135
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:48,970
Let's invite her

136
00:07:49,050 --> 00:07:49,970
to lunch.

137
00:07:50,890 --> 00:07:52,470
Don't give up halfway, okay?

138
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,480
Chen Jing'an,

139
00:08:07,050 --> 00:08:09,050
let's have lunch together.

140
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,520
Okay.

141
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,260
And me! I'm joining you.

142
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:20,690
Tian Ye,

143
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:25,390
I need to talk to you.

144
00:08:30,050 --> 00:08:31,350
How's your nose?

145
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,100
Doesn't hurt much now.

146
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:34,940
Good.

147
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:42,390
What happened?

148
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:43,470
Eye pain?

149
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:45,190
Niannian,

150
00:08:45,350 --> 00:08:47,140
ask her to help with the connection.

151
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:48,510
What connection?

152
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,350
Never mind, I'll help you.

153
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,600
Chen Jing'an,

154
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,760
try this dish.

155
00:08:55,930 --> 00:08:57,010
It's delicious.

156
00:08:57,970 --> 00:08:58,850
Thank you.

157
00:08:58,850 --> 00:08:59,690
Do you know

158
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:02,100
what Chen Changning wants from Tian Ye?

159
00:09:03,470 --> 00:09:04,470
I don't know.

160
00:09:04,970 --> 00:09:06,340
Why do you care?

161
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:07,550
It doesn't affect our meal.

162
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:13,940
Who kicked me?

163
00:09:16,410 --> 00:09:17,290
Chen Jing'an,

164
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,970
your brother's outstanding.

165
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,140
He must have many admirers.

166
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,760
Do you help them
deliver love letters?

167
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,600
No way.

168
00:09:23,850 --> 00:09:26,180
She wouldn't do something so tacky.

169
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:27,910
Right,

170
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:29,600
I've never done that.

171
00:09:30,850 --> 00:09:31,690
I see.

172
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:34,100
You know,

173
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:37,050
Chen Changning is like a fashion model.

174
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,390
Even this plain school uniform

175
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:40,010
looks tailored on him.

176
00:09:40,010 --> 00:09:41,200
And look at Niannian,

177
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,850
she's also like a model.

178
00:09:43,010 --> 00:09:44,800
They'd look great together,

179
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:46,890
like a couple.

180
00:09:46,930 --> 00:09:47,830
I think...

181
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:50,550
Here, try this. It's good.

182
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,970
Alright, alright.

183
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:00,140
At our school,

184
00:10:00,430 --> 00:10:01,720
many girls

185
00:10:01,970 --> 00:10:03,100
like Chen Changning,

186
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:04,600
but none are good enough

187
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,850
for him.

188
00:10:05,890 --> 00:10:07,300
The only one

189
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:08,140
who matches him...

190
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,550
- Are you okay?
- You okay?

191
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:12,720
Chen Jing'an.

192
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:14,140
Have some soup.

193
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,560
Okay.

194
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:20,300
Where was I?

195
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,050
Oh, Chen Changning...

196
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,930
How many times

197
00:10:23,930 --> 00:10:25,050
have you mentioned him?

198
00:10:25,050 --> 00:10:26,220
Using him as seasoning?

199
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:27,720
- But...
- Alright, alright.

200
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:29,260
Let's eat.

201
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,720
The bell will ring soon.

202
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,440
No more.

203
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:06,850
I quit.

204
00:11:07,140 --> 00:11:07,980
Exhausted.

205
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:10,680
I skipped breakfast

206
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,350
just to get beaten by you.

207
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:15,300
I need to ask you something.

208
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:16,390
What?

209
00:11:18,050 --> 00:11:18,890
You beat me

210
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:20,300
just to ask questions?

211
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,930
Had to make you talk.

212
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:27,520
What is it?

213
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:29,520
I'll tell you

214
00:11:29,970 --> 00:11:30,810
everything

215
00:11:31,220 --> 00:11:32,060
I know.

216
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,890
When my mom hits me again,

217
00:11:34,930 --> 00:11:36,180
can I reach out to you?

218
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:44,270
Back to the topic.

219
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:47,180
Chen Jing'an's been acting strange.

220
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:49,140
I feel like

221
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,800
she's been gentler.

222
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:52,520
Not the point.

223
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:55,100
What's her relationship

224
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,600
with Li Minqiu?

225
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,060
Basketball friends.

226
00:11:58,760 --> 00:11:59,890
They met through games.

227
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,440
Why do you ask?

228
00:12:02,010 --> 00:12:03,550
There's nothing shady going on?

229
00:12:03,970 --> 00:12:04,810
Shady?

230
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,510
What could be shady?

231
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,300
I suspect they're dating.

232
00:12:14,890 --> 00:12:15,730
No way.

233
00:12:16,390 --> 00:12:17,550
Chen Jing'an and Li Minqiu?

234
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,930
There is no way.

235
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,140
Are you sure?

236
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,130
Do you know

237
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:30,270
who bought your yogurt?

238
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,450
Chen Jing'an.

239
00:12:31,570 --> 00:12:32,600
No, it was Li Minqiu.

240
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:39,890
How...

241
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,130
How could that be?

242
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:44,140
She said she bought it for me.

243
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,800
She told me you bought it

244
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:47,800
to hide the fact

245
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,600
that it was Li Minqiu.

246
00:12:58,390 --> 00:12:59,230
They...

247
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:02,140
How could they...

248
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,800
How could Chen Jing'an like him?

249
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:07,800
You need to pick the right side.

250
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:10,220
Don't cover for Chen Jing'an.

251
00:13:11,180 --> 00:13:12,850
Tell me immediately if you have updates.

252
00:13:13,430 --> 00:13:14,270
Got it?

253
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,720
So you want me

254
00:13:15,970 --> 00:13:17,140
to be a spy?

255
00:13:17,430 --> 00:13:18,270
No,

256
00:13:20,140 --> 00:13:20,980
an informant.

257
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:26,640
Alright.

258
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:28,680
I'll keep an eye on Chen Jing'an.

259
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:30,890
We can't let her

260
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:32,550
go up the wrong path.

261
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:35,220
It's "go down".

262
00:13:40,140 --> 00:13:41,430
You know what I mean.

263
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:52,800
Goodbye, sir.

264
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:54,510
Goodbye, class.

265
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:08,640
Why that look?

266
00:14:08,930 --> 00:14:09,770
Chen Jing'an,

267
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:12,390
I heard a story recently.

268
00:14:16,090 --> 00:14:18,010
Aren't you curious?

269
00:14:19,050 --> 00:14:20,050
No.

270
00:14:20,510 --> 00:14:21,970
Then let me tell you,

271
00:14:22,640 --> 00:14:23,480
it's about

272
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,440
a native schoolgirl

273
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:26,100
who ignored

274
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:28,760
all warnings

275
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,890
from her friends and family

276
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:31,090
and got tricked

277
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:32,300
by a gutter guy's

278
00:14:33,640 --> 00:14:34,480
sweet talk.

279
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:35,980
She lost her money,

280
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:37,640
her virtue,

281
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,050
and got disfigured.

282
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:41,640
Car accident...

283
00:14:42,100 --> 00:14:42,940
Abortion...

284
00:14:44,370 --> 00:14:45,680
She was abandoned by all

285
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,800
and died full of regrets.

286
00:14:48,850 --> 00:14:49,690
That's...

287
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:51,140
so tragic.

288
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:54,140
You even believed such a fake story.

289
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:56,220
We live in a law-based society.

290
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:58,220
Such a thing is not allowed.

291
00:14:58,470 --> 00:15:00,350
There are still many delinquents.

292
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,390
What if?

293
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:05,430
Not in this area.

294
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:07,850
Are you sure?

295
00:15:08,710 --> 00:15:09,680
I think

296
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:12,140
Li Minqiu

297
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:13,890
is exactly that type.

298
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,100
No way.

299
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:17,420
Li Minqiu

300
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:19,300
seems unfriendly,

301
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:20,760
but he's actually nice.

