00:15:27,350 --> 00:15:28,190
(Oh no...)

304
00:15:28,890 --> 00:15:32,470
(She's been completely brainwashed.)

305
00:15:33,890 --> 00:15:36,050
(How to save you,)

306
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:38,510
(my friend?)

307
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:50,140
Niannian.

308
00:15:51,930 --> 00:15:52,850
Li Minqiu.

309
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,190
Why are you here?

310
00:15:54,190 --> 00:15:55,510
And in our school uniform.

311
00:15:56,050 --> 00:15:57,720
I borrowed it to see you.

312
00:15:58,220 --> 00:15:59,400
We haven't met in years.

313
00:15:59,490 --> 00:16:00,390
How are you?

314
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,140
I... I'm okay.

315
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:05,600
After seeing you yesterday,

316
00:16:05,890 --> 00:16:06,760
I couldn't sleep

317
00:16:06,850 --> 00:16:08,290
