318
00:16:08,430 --> 00:16:10,100
No wonder you got dark circles.

319
00:16:10,970 --> 00:16:11,810
For your health,

320
00:16:12,010 --> 00:16:13,470
you should sleep early.

321
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:14,840
Niannian,

322
00:16:15,430 --> 00:16:16,970
you still care about me.

323
00:16:17,230 --> 00:16:18,300
When we were kids,

324
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:20,020
once after I got in a fight,

325
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:22,600
you cried but still put band-aids on me.

326
00:16:23,850 --> 00:16:26,390
(I'm not Zhu Niannian.
