330
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,160
I have homework.

331
00:16:33,170 --> 00:16:34,040
Let me walk you back.

332
00:16:35,970 --> 00:16:36,810
Li Minqiu,

333
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,930
