334
00:16:38,970 --> 00:16:39,810
Why are you here?

335
00:16:40,010 --> 00:16:41,550
What is it to you?

336
00:16:41,970 --> 00:16:43,360
I'm the student council president.

337
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,100
It's my business

338
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:46,300
to take care of

339
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:47,220
