343
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:58,050
Listen,

344
00:16:58,050 --> 00:16:59,550
stay away from Chen Jing'an

345
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,180
and don't come back ever.

346
00:17:02,850 --> 00:17:03,690
You...

347
00:17:04,300 --> 00:17:05,510
You're so bossy.

348
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:07,100
I'm here for her.

349
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:08,140
Move.

350
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:10,890
Last warning,

351
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:12,430
leave now.

352
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,350
Fine.

353
00:17:15,510 --> 00:17:16,430
I'll go today.

354
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:18,430
But I'll come back

355
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:19,970
with my men.

356
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,550
Niannian, bye.

357
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:30,390
(What was that?)

358
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:33,680
(Chen Changning playing the hero?)

359
00:17:40,220 --> 00:17:41,140
Thank you,

360
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:42,390
Changning.

361
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:44,300
If he bothers you again,

362
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:45,470
let me know.

363
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:47,720
Stay away from people

364
00:17:48,220 --> 00:17:49,180
like Li Minqiu.

365
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:50,470
Don't be fooled.

366
00:17:50,930 --> 00:17:51,770
Fooled?

367
00:17:52,510 --> 00:17:54,510
He's just a bit annoying,

368
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:55,550
not a scammer.

369
00:17:57,430 --> 00:17:58,760
His kind

370
00:17:59,350 --> 00:18:00,760
