379
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:34,470
If Li Minqiu bothers you again,

380
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:35,680
I can help you.

381
00:18:37,100 --> 00:18:37,940
Oh,

382
00:18:38,390 --> 00:18:40,080
