385
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:44,300
from him.

386
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:47,640
Alright.

387
00:18:50,180 --> 00:18:51,800
(Unprovoked kindness.)

388
00:18:52,350 --> 00:18:54,600
(Doesn't seem like his style.)

389
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:56,860
(Could it be)

390
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,600
(he has feelings for Zhu Niannian?)

391
00:19:00,930 --> 00:19:01,800
Zhu Niannian,

392
00:19:02,390 --> 00:19:03,230
