393
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:06,640
I have things to do.

394
00:19:06,930 --> 00:19:07,770
See you.

395
00:19:36,390 --> 00:19:37,230
Chen Jing'an,

396
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,510
here's the thing.

397
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:41,390
I think

398
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:42,680
your brother's words

399
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:44,760
aren't all unreasonable.

400
00:19:44,970 --> 00:19:45,970
We should listen

401
00:19:46,220 --> 00:19:47,060
to what we ought to,

402
00:19:47,300 --> 00:19:48,140
and even to

403
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:49,020
what we shouldn't.

404
00:19:49,970 --> 00:19:50,930
As for my words,

405
00:19:50,930 --> 00:19:52,640
like they say, "Ignore Tian Ye's advice,

406
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:53,890
and you'll regret."

407
00:19:54,140 --> 00:19:55,390
I really don't want you

408
00:19:55,970 --> 00:19:58,050
to suffer unnecessary losses,

409
00:19:58,100 --> 00:19:58,940
