415
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,560
Zhu Niannian.

416
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:11,800
Chen Jing'an, a word.

417
00:20:12,010 --> 00:20:12,850
Come with me.

418
00:20:16,930 --> 00:20:17,950
What's your relationship

419
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:19,510
with Li Minqiu when you were kids?

420
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:21,100
If he comes to me again,

421
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:21,940
what should I do?

422
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,560
We were neighbors as kids,

423
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,070
played together a lot.

424
00:20:27,180 --> 00:20:28,680
He took good care of me.

425
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:30,220
After he moved away,

426
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:31,890
we lost touch.

427
00:20:32,220 --> 00:20:33,600
Don't worry too much.

428
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,550
If he brings up the past,

429
00:20:35,550 --> 00:20:37,260
just say you forgot.

430
00:20:37,970 --> 00:20:39,600
It's been years.

431
00:20:39,890 --> 00:20:41,600
Even if you slip up,

432
00:20:41,850 --> 00:20:43,470
he probably won't notice.

433
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:44,350
That works.

434
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:45,850
He came to see me today,

435
00:20:45,850 --> 00:20:46,930
and said all those things.

436
00:20:47,010 --> 00:20:48,600
I had no idea how to respond.

437
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:49,930
I was scared I'd mess up.

438
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:51,140
Luckily,

439
00:20:51,140 --> 00:20:53,010
Chen Changning chased Li Minqiu off.

440
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:55,350
Chen Changning chased him off?

441
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:56,290
Yeah.

442
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:57,120
He also said

443
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:58,470
