444
00:20:58,890 --> 00:20:59,770
Like,

445
00:20:59,780 --> 00:21:01,220
"Don't be fooled",

446
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,510
"Many two-timers",

447
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:03,790
and all that.

448
00:21:04,050 --> 00:21:06,190
Now that you mention it,

449
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:08,430
Tian Ye acted strange too.

450
00:21:08,930 --> 00:21:10,550
Earlier, he kept hinting about

451
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,140
