to stay away from Li Minqiu.

455
00:21:20,890 --> 00:21:23,640
Today, Tian Ye drops these hints...

456
00:21:24,930 --> 00:21:26,010
Do they seriously think

457
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,800
I'm dating Li Minqiu?

458
00:21:28,430 --> 00:21:29,430
You and Li Minqiu?

459
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:32,790
Wait, it's you

460
00:21:33,140 --> 00:21:34,220
and Li Minqiu.

461
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:35,550
