462
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,980
Their imaginations are wild enough

463
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:37,850
to write novels!

464
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:42,640
It must've been a misunderstanding
from yesterday.

465
00:21:43,390 --> 00:21:45,430
I'll talk to Minqiu about this

466
00:21:45,430 --> 00:21:46,760
and have him clear things up.

467
00:21:46,930 --> 00:21:48,490
