468
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:49,780
My flawless reputation

469
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:51,200
can't be ruined like this.

470
00:21:51,390 --> 00:21:53,010
Also, tell him not to look for me

471
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:53,920
at school anymore.

472
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:55,470
And I'm Zhu Niannian right now.

473
00:21:55,950 --> 00:21:57,510
Your reputation can't be ruined either.

474
00:21:58,010 --> 00:21:58,850
Got it?

475
00:22:09,350 --> 00:22:10,190
Five.

476
00:22:10,390 --> 00:22:11,230
Four.

477
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:13,430
Three, two, one.

478
00:22:13,470 --> 00:22:14,310
Time's up.

479
00:22:17,080 --> 00:22:17,920
Forty-five.

480
00:22:22,430 --> 00:22:23,550
- How many?
- Forty-five.

481
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:26,510
Changning, done?

482
00:22:26,930 --> 00:22:27,890
I'm exhausted.

483
00:22:27,930 --> 00:22:28,770
Sir,

484
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:30,970
here you go.

485
00:22:32,140 --> 00:22:33,800
Take these soccer balls back

486
00:22:33,890 --> 00:22:34,730
