496
00:22:56,870 --> 00:22:57,710
Done!

497
00:22:59,430 --> 00:23:00,270
Shasha.

498
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,560
Why?

499
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,100
Niannian, I'll open the door

500
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:04,110
in fifteen minutes.

501
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:06,030
Shasha. Shasha.

502
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:20,220
Why are you here?

503
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:21,470
To return the balls.

504
00:23:22,850 --> 00:23:23,890
Why did she lock the door?

505
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:26,980
Prank.

506
00:23:28,140 --> 00:23:29,140
It'll open soon.

507
00:23:29,510 --> 00:23:31,300
I'll deal with her when I'm out.

508
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:32,440
It's fine.

509
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:33,760
I'm not busy anyway.

510
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,850
If you're not in a hurry,

511
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:37,890
I actually have something to say.

512
00:23:45,140 --> 00:23:45,980
Alright then.

513
00:23:46,470 --> 00:23:47,470
Go ahead.

514
00:23:49,050 --> 00:23:49,890
Zhu Niannian,

515
00:23:50,930 --> 00:23:52,360
actually, I'm a bit curious

516
00:23:53,100 --> 00:23:54,890
how did you become friends with Jing'an?

517
00:23:55,390 --> 00:23:57,140
The reason we became friends

518
00:23:57,350 --> 00:23:58,190
is...

519
00:24:00,510 --> 00:24:02,350
