527
00:24:14,260 --> 00:24:15,830
That's just them being blind.

528
00:24:18,220 --> 00:24:19,100
I, Zhu Niannian,

529
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:20,430
am not like that.

530
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:22,550
You don't think

531
00:24:23,390 --> 00:24:25,010
