532
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:27,270
Not exactly.

533
00:24:31,010 --> 00:24:32,140
If you ask me,

534
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:34,100
you just don't understand Chen Jing'an.

535
00:24:35,600 --> 00:24:36,510
Why do you say that?

536
00:24:37,930 --> 00:24:38,770
Then tell me,

537
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,760
what do you think of her?

538
00:24:44,190 --> 00:24:45,050
Although she seems

539
00:24:45,050 --> 00:24:46,180
like a tomboy,

540
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:47,680
rough around the edges,

541
00:24:48,550 --> 00:24:49,800
she's actually thoughtful.

542
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:52,890
And she acts on impulse.

543
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,890
Once she's set on something,

544
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,140
no one can stop her.

545
00:24:58,970 --> 00:24:59,810
Wait...

546
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:01,890
are you praising her

547
00:25:02,300 --> 00:25:03,140
or criticizing her?

548
00:25:03,140 --> 00:25:04,760
I...I'm a little confused.

549
00:25:04,970 --> 00:25:05,970
It's hard to say

550
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:08,100
if her personality is good or bad.

551
00:25:09,260 --> 00:25:11,050
If she meets the right people,

552
00:25:11,470 --> 00:25:12,470
of course it's good.

553
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,300
But if she misjudges someone,

554
00:25:16,260 --> 00:25:17,760
it'll only hurt her in the end.

555
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:20,140
It's not that serious, is it?

556
00:25:20,970 --> 00:25:23,180
I think Chen Jing'an has good judgment.

557
00:25:23,510 --> 00:25:24,470
Good judgment?

558
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:26,390
You mean Li Minqiu?

559
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,390
I...

560
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:30,440
Well,

561
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:31,800
what happened?

562
00:25:33,390 --> 00:25:34,370
I suspect they're dating.

563
00:25:34,370 --> 00:25:35,300
No way.

564
00:25:36,390 --> 00:25:37,230
I...

565
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,640
I promise you,

566
00:25:38,930 --> 00:25:39,770
there's no way

567
00:25:39,970 --> 00:25:42,100
she likes Li Minqiu.

568
00:25:42,260 --> 00:25:43,260
How can you be so sure?

569
00:25:44,390 --> 00:25:45,300
You know something?

570
00:25:45,470 --> 00:25:46,310
I...

571
00:25:47,390 --> 00:25:48,880
I don't know how to explain it,

572
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:50,970
but trust me on this.

573
00:25:50,970 --> 00:25:52,260
Chen Jing'an would never

574
00:25:52,260 --> 00:25:53,460
like Li Minqiu.

575
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,800
So it's Li Minqiu
having a one-sided crush.

576
00:25:56,450 --> 00:25:58,720
Why can't you get this?

577
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,760
Then… what about Tian Ye?

578
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:02,070
Will they be together?

579
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:02,980
No way.

580
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:04,850
She's never seen him as a guy.

581
00:26:05,340 --> 00:26:06,730
Exactly.

582
00:26:06,890 --> 00:26:07,970
And Li Minqiu

583
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:09,510
is even less likely than Tian Ye.

584
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:11,930
That's for the best.

585
00:26:17,850 --> 00:26:18,690
Zhu Niannian,

586
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:22,070
honestly, I'm really glad

587
00:26:22,430 --> 00:26:23,720
you two became friends.

588
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:28,850
Our family is special.

589
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,050
Our parents are busy with work.

590
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:34,300
She basically grew up
with just me around.

591
00:26:34,350 --> 00:26:35,510
She's been strong-willed

592
00:26:36,510 --> 00:26:37,510
but also insecure.

593
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:40,050
Sometimes she's snappy,

594
00:26:40,850 --> 00:26:42,300
especially to people close to her.

